Package com.yantra.api.ypm.pricelist

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    copyPricelist
    Copy a price list.
    getPricelistHeaderDetails
    Retrieve details of a price list.
    getPricelistHeaderList
    Retrieve list of price list headers.
    getPricelistLineList
    Retrieve list of price list lines.
    getPricelistLineListForItem
    Retrieves list of price list lines for all the items specified in the search criteria.
    managePricelistHeader
    Create, modify or delete a price list.
    managePricelistLine
    Create, modify or delete one or more price list lines.
    massManagePricelistLine
    Perform bulk update or delete on price list lines.
